    <item>
      <title>Villeroy说，欧洲央行的存款率可能为2％。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/ecb-deposit-rate-could-be-2-in-the-summer-villeroy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[理事会成员弗朗索瓦·维罗伊·德·加尔胡（Francois Villeroy de Galhau）表示，削减可能会使欧洲央行的利率提高到今年夏天的2％，但除此之外，这并没有明确的方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/ecb-deposit-rate-could-be-2-in-the-summer-villeroy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡人说，预算还不足以管理成本上升，民意调查发现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/singapore-budget-not-enough-to-manage-rising-costs-poll-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，大多数新加坡居民认为，最新年度预算中的措施是不足以帮助他们应对生活成本上升的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/singapore-budget-not-enough-to-manage-rising-costs-poll-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 04:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
